<div class="thumb tleft">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:152px;"><a href="/wiki/File:KidsindoorwayC.jpg" class="image" title="Children in Jerusalem"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/cc/KidsindoorwayC.jpg/150px-KidsindoorwayC.jpg" width="150" height="130" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
