<li><a href="http://etext.lib.virginia.edu/cgi-local/DHI/dhi.cgi?id=dv1-73" class="external text" title="http://etext.lib.virginia.edu/cgi-local/DHI/dhi.cgi?id=dv1-73" rel="nofollow">Dictionary of the History of Ideas</a> "culture" and "civilization" in modern times</li>
<li><a href="http://global-culture.org/" class="external text" title="http://global-culture.org/" rel="nofollow">Global Culture</a> Essays on global issues and their impact on culture</li>
